entries.femaleVariant: Graphite-woven for extra durability – real fuckin' next level shit.
Got your back done – couldn't toss in an arm while you were at it?
My bro did these tats. Kind of a shame.
So? I know a guy who can weave syn-skin to spec with anything you want.
Arms, legs, doesn't matter. Mikey's got a whole wall of that shit.
Mikey, pff... Sounds just like him.
No, but seriously, who came up with "glitter?"
Shut up...
I mean, what a gonk name. We selling skez for kids, now?
For crying out loud. It was s'posed to be "neon" but that was already taken.
Fucking brilliant.
Who cares? Shit sells.
<kiroshi l="jpn" o="シロウの分はもう確保してあるんだっけ" t="You put these aside for Shiro?" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="jpn" o="ああ、15キロ分をリトル・クーロンに送ってある" t="Dozen plus three bricks. On their way to Little Kowloon now." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="jpn" o="チューマ、少しは羽目外そうぜ。ウチは今絶好調じゃねえか" t="Chooms, we need to cut loose. We're on the up and up now." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="jpn" o="売れに売れてる。アガリを数えるのが追いつかねえ！" t="Stuff sells quicker than I can count our in-flow." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="jpn" o="追いついてないのは、生産の方だ。そうやってうつつを抜かす前に――" t="Boys, you can dream big all we want, but this shit needs synthesizing." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="jpn" o="ヘヘ… 科学者先生が秘密のレシピさえ教えてくれりゃな…" t="He, he, he. If only the master chemist would share his secret formula..." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="jpn" o="そうすりゃ後は…" t="We'd just have to..." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="jpn" o="またその話か？ しつこいぞ" t="We've discussed it already. Drop it." b="" a=""/>
"Cooome get your glitter! Brighten up that smile!"
So now it's "glitter."
<kiroshi l="jpn" o="まずはしっかり働け" t="Then you can grow a pair." b="" a=""/>
